Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.62,variety,,0,0,0,,Chosen by parents! My son is shining in this theory! Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.39,variety,,0,0,0,,The next guests are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:12.29,variety,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:15.16,variety,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us today, thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.46,variety,,0,0,0,,I'm Kurokawa Kaori
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:21.17,variety,,0,0,0,,I'm his wife, Kurokawa Miyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.47,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1404,279)}I see where this is going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:27.57,variety,,0,0,0,,They are the parents of Kurokawa Akihito, more commonly known as Kurochan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:24.80,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1404,303)}This is the first time\NI saw his parents
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:30.41,variety,,0,0,0,,Kurochan, who has participated in 32 theories, up till now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:37.68,variety,,0,0,0,,Additionally, involved in various themes such as Monster house and Monster idol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.35,variety,,0,0,0,,I've actually been watching all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.22,variety,,0,0,0,,I've been watching it as well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:48.19,variety,,0,0,0,,But my heart somehow feels disgusted sometimes, seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.36,variety,,0,0,0,,He always does weird things, right? Such as lying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:56.10,variety,,0,0,0,,When I see those things, my heart aches
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:03.44,variety,,0,0,0,,First of all, let's see which theory does\Nshe thinks her son is shining the most
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:09.28,variety,,0,0,0,,I personally like the theory about the race between pigeon and human the most
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:12.62,variety,,0,0,0,,Because he didn't say anything strange in that episode
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:18.36,variety,,0,0,0,,So that one gave me a good impression
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:18.36,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1404,303)}Kurochan's mother\Nis an earnest person
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:25.86,variety,,0,0,0,,Pigeon and human, starting from a random location
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:29.13,variety,,0,0,0,,Who will the one to arrive home first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:33.81,variety,,0,0,0,,Theory: In terms of homing instinct, humans can do better than pigeons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:39.11,variety,,0,0,0,,Since he doesn't have any cash on him, so I thought he will rack his brain to think of a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:44.02,variety,,0,0,0,,But then, he still ends up using some nasty tricks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:50.59,variety,,0,0,0,,Exactly. To ensure a fair race with the pigeons, Kurochan's wallet and smartphone have been confiscate, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.09,variety,,0,0,0,,I'll take this, thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.49,variety,,0,0,0,,I'll make good use of the money you gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:02:00.57,variety,,0,0,0,,He held a photography event on the spot, \Nand earned enough money to buy a train ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:03.64,variety,,0,0,0,,I'm going back home with the help from everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:06.71,variety,,0,0,0,,He has always been like this since childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:11.51,variety,,0,0,0,,Don't know if he is clever or cunning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:19.52,variety,,0,0,0,,In regard to money, Kurochan has been demonstrating his cunning cleverness since childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.79,variety,,0,0,0,,When he borrowed money from his younger sister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.49,variety,,0,0,0,,Although a normal people will pay back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:29.90,variety,,0,0,0,,However, that kid has been thinking about excuses to not pay back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:34.40,variety,,0,0,0,,And he said "I'll let you be my elder sister, so give me money please"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:40.41,variety,,0,0,0,,So he means that he's now the younger one, and his younger sister is now his elder sister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.54,variety,,0,0,0,,And because she's now the elder one, she should give him money
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:46.31,variety,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what he's talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:53.62,variety,,0,0,0,,The story continues, Kurochan's cunning cleverness escalated when he became an university student
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.62,variety-left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1031,300)}-He's pissing me off\N-Sure he is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.69,variety,,0,0,0,,When he's 22 years old?   -Yeah, around 20 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:00.29,variety,,0,0,0,,He said he want to get a hair transplant   -Yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:07.40,variety,,0,0,0,,He said he wants to get a hair transplant, and asked us to give him money
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.97,variety,,0,0,0,,Around four hundred thousand yen...   -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.54,variety,,0,0,0,,Did he really get a hair transplant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.61,variety,,0,0,0,,I don't think so   -No idea, he never mentioned it again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.21,variety,,0,0,0,,All he did was taking money away from us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.21,variety,,0,0,0,,He's probably good at asking for a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.25,variety,,0,0,0,,But I believe he's not doing these kinds of thing to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.65,variety,,0,0,0,,Hopefully he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.79,variety,,0,0,0,,I told him not to do these things to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.09,variety,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when it comes to money
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.66,variety,,0,0,0,,So this is Kurochan, someone who is obsessed with money
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:35.76,variety,,0,0,0,,Even when he became a comedian, he has been asking for money from his parents until recently
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.66,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1399,304)}He really looks\Nlike a bad guy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:35.79,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1405,272)}Until very recently
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:40.27,variety,,0,0,0,,Before he was 30 years old, he asked for $150,000 yen per month
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:46.94,variety,,0,0,0,,He asked for $50,000 yen per month after that,\Nonly until 2 years ago, when he reached 42 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.47,variety,,0,0,0,,Which has been a famous story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:55.15,variety,,0,0,0,,We told him not to borrow money from other people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.55,variety,,0,0,0,,When it comes to money, just rely on us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.55,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1405,272)}His parents are really kind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.15,variety,,0,0,0,,Therefore that guy is living an elegant lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.69,variety,,0,0,0,,When I was on a business trip in Tokyo, and went to meet him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.53,variety,,0,0,0,,I asked him "where are you going now?" and he said "I am going to the beauty salon"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:12.30,variety,,0,0,0,,And I thought how dare you go to those\Nplaces? You don't even have money
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.47,variety,,0,0,0,,Back to today's theme
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:20.51,variety,,0,0,0,,Which theory does Kurochan's father thinks his son is shining the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.68,variety,,0,0,0,,Well, probably the "Future Kurochan"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.85,variety,,0,0,0,,I'm able to watch it and laugh the whole way through it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:31.45,variety,,0,0,0,,The man's lie and love being trifled with prophetic tweets
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:37.99,variety,,0,0,0,,Being under complete surveillance for 10 days, the documentary "Future Kurochan"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:42.23,variety,,0,0,0,,Let's sit down and then talk   -Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:48.30,variety,,0,0,0,,The pitfall is of course in front of the bench
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.30,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,316.143)}He's got to know\Nthat it's there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:54.67,variety,,0,0,0,,From how Rei-chama is positioned, it's clear Kurochan appears to suspect something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:05:04.28,variety,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about how great you really are, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:09.29,variety,,0,0,0,,This whole week I was thinking about how great you are, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:14.19,variety,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking if I like you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.86,variety,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.33,variety,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to put that out there clearly   -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.83,variety,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.83,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1348,317.142)}He means that\N"I'm believing you"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:28.04,variety,,0,0,0,,I really do like you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.04,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1348,348)}He's gonna be\Ndouble shocked if\Nthere's indeed a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:36.38,variety,,0,0,0,,So, let's sit down and talk   -Yes, let's sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:47.13,variety,,0,0,0,,This is heartbreaking   -So heartbreaking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.83,variety,,0,0,0,,She's running off   -Truly heartbreaking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.40,variety,,0,0,0,,She's running! She's running!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.50,variety,,0,0,0,,She's hopping away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.50,variety,,0,0,0,,This must be traumatizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.84,variety,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this gonna result in trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.08,variety,,0,0,0,,Isn't he crying already? Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:10.48,variety,,0,0,0,,Kurochan, hang in there   -Climb on out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:13.95,variety,,0,0,0,,Good things will happen   -Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.52,variety,,0,0,0,,Kurochan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:20.36,variety,,0,0,0,,I can't watch this, come on...   -This is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.26,variety,,0,0,0,,This is just...too heartbreaking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.40,variety,,0,0,0,,I can't look at this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.83,variety,,0,0,0,,Climbing out from there like that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:34.71,variety,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's gone, Rei-chama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:43.05,variety,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is Rainy Blue's playing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.49,variety,,0,0,0,,He's not saying a thing   -Not a word
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.39,variety,,0,0,0,,This is truly heartbreaking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.93,variety,,0,0,0,,He got on alone   -This really went too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.47,variety,,0,0,0,,He came with another person, but is leaving alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:15.21,variety,,0,0,0,,Such an epic film   -Even the greatest actor won't be able to make this face
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:18.38,variety,,0,0,0,,I like that face   -You're good, Kurochan, you're fine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.02,variety,,0,0,0,,Still filming even when he arrives home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.16,variety,,0,0,0,,This is really something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:34.23,variety,,0,0,0,,Those good memories, look at his happy face
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.84,variety,,0,0,0,,He stored it at his home, huh?   -From the matching pair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.91,variety,,0,0,0,,He's looking at it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.95,variety,,0,0,0,,What's he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.39,variety,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.52,variety,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.96,variety,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello, Sae-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.17,variety,,0,0,0,,Sae-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.17,variety,,0,0,0,,Eh? A different girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.24,variety,,0,0,0,,Do you like meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:18.08,variety,,0,0,0,,And the most memorable scene in Future Kurochan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:26.45,variety,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370.286,494.429)}Rei-chama's glass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.56,variety,,0,0,0,,Everything went just as we imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:37.76,variety,,0,0,0,,I hate it, that's nasty, licking someone else's things
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:41.87,variety,,0,0,0,,As Kurochan's mother, how do you feel when you see him licking the glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.70,variety,,0,0,0,,I feel like vomiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:51.94,variety,,0,0,0,,I start to wonder am I really the one who gave birth to this kid, seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.41,variety,,0,0,0,,And I thought "so this kid is doing these kinds of thing"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.98,variety,,0,0,0,,"No wonder he's not attractive to women"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:09:01.55,variety,,0,0,0,,"Because he's doing these kinds of thing, and being aired on TV"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:05.72,variety,,0,0,0,,And in regard to this "glass licking act"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:12.00,variety,,0,0,0,,Kurochan's nieces are very disgusted as well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.43,variety,,0,0,0,,They say he is no different from a scumbag
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:20.27,variety,,0,0,0,,And call him "shit" and "bastard"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.77,variety,,0,0,0,,How did you feel when you hear them call him with those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.84,variety,,0,0,0,,I was really angry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:29.01,variety,,0,0,0,,Why should he be scolded by you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.21,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1399.429,306.857)}Oh, so she's on\NKurochan's side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:34.95,variety,,0,0,0,,So I stood on my son's side, and chewed my granddaughters up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.52,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1407.143,303.429)}Ah, of course, he's\NKurochan's mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:40.46,variety,,0,0,0,,Although he's a scumbag, he's still her son, who she gave birth in pain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.46,variety-right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1402,310.286)}Don't call him\Na scumbag
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:45.13,variety,,0,0,0,,She's angry even if the ones who scolded him are their relatives
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.60,variety,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:50.74,variety,,0,0,0,,Some other comedians call him "baldy"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:55.64,variety,,0,0,0,,Whenever others talk bad about him on tv shows, I can't help but feel angry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:01.45,variety,,0,0,0,,Thereafter, I will never watch any shows with that comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.55,variety,,0,0,0,,Whenever he appears, I'll change the channel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.32,variety,,0,0,0,,She definitely dislikes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:09.39,variety,,0,0,0,,For example, which comedian talked bad about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.72,variety,,0,0,0,,Everyone, right?   -Yeah, everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:17.10,variety,,0,0,0,,Not much people is treating him nice, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.33,variety,,0,0,0,,What if you have to choose one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.33,variety,,0,0,0,,Fujimon?   -Fujimon-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:28.57,variety,,0,0,0,,So in conclusion, these are the two theories that Kurochan's parents think their son shined the most
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:28.34,variety-left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(416.572,251)}In terms of homing instinct,\Nhumans can do better than pigeons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:28.34,variety,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,823.572)}Future Kurochan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:35.11,variety,,0,0,0,,Given this precious chance to meet his parents, we've decided to ask a bunch more questions about Kurochan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:53.50,variety,,0,0,0,,Is he a restless sleeper since childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.50,variety,,0,0,0,,Well, I know he snores very loudly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.94,variety,,0,0,0,,But I never saw him tossing and turning when he sleeps at home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:03.78,variety,,0,0,0,,So I didn't know about this until I saw it on TV, and I thought "that's terrible"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:08.71,variety,,0,0,0,,Is his room very untidy since childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.82,variety,,0,0,0,,No, no, not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:14.65,variety,,0,0,0,,He has been living with his sister in the same room, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.86,variety,,0,0,0,,So he's probably showing his true color after he left home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.62,variety,,0,0,0,,No one will come
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.16,variety,,0,0,0,,With complete freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:26.43,variety,,0,0,0,,When did he start having hairs on his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.47,variety,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1296,305.857)}Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.87,variety,,0,0,0,,I never saw him naked
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.54,variety,,0,0,0,,So when I saw that on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.97,variety,,0,0,0,,I thought like "Eh?..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:37.11,variety,,0,0,0,,It must be disgusting to sleep with that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.48,variety,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I know nothing about him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.11,variety,,0,0,0,,He didn't have hairs before   -On his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:49.29,variety,,0,0,0,,But come on, it couldn't be gene mutation though
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:53.19,variety,,0,0,0,,By the way, does Kurochan's father have hairs on his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.73,variety,,0,0,0,,I don't have hairs on my back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:01.67,variety,,0,0,0,,Including all our relatives, Akihito (Kurochan) is the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:07.67,variety,,0,0,0,,Does he cry a lot since childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.67,variety,,0,0,0,,That thing cries all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.44,variety,,0,0,0,,He cries every time I scold him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:14.41,variety,,0,0,0,,Whenever we say like "Did you do this?" or "That's no good"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.72,variety,,0,0,0,,Then he will cry and say sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.35,variety,,0,0,0,,Well, he's probably fake crying though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.35,variety,,0,0,0,,That thing is malicious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:27.29,variety,,0,0,0,,How else is he different from others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.66,variety,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1234.286,299)}They are so mean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:32.33,variety,,0,0,0,,He was conspicuous during secondary school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:36.53,variety,,0,0,0,,While everyone else is wearing shoes, only Akihito is not wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.34,variety,,0,0,0,,Because he don't like wearing socks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:42.71,variety,,0,0,0,,When others told me "What happened, Ms Kurokawa? Your son is barefooted"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:45.44,variety,,0,0,0,,I was like "Eh?..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:49.48,variety,,0,0,0,,I was shocked, I'm always getting shocked by him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:55.25,variety,,0,0,0,,Young Kurochan showed so many facets to his personality, which even shocked his own parents, furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:13:01.53,variety,,0,0,0,,What was his future career plan when he was a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:04.23,variety,,0,0,0,,His high school teacher asked him about this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:06.73,variety,,0,0,0,,And he said "I want to become a hero", a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:11.50,variety,,0,0,0,,He said "I want train myself in China, and stay in some remote mountain"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.77,variety,,0,0,0,,"And I'll soon become a hero"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:16.07,variety,,0,0,0,,This guy is unbelievable...   -He's already in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:21.68,variety,,0,0,0,,Then his teacher told him "there's no jobs for hero, there's no such occupation"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.68,variety,,0,0,0,,His teacher told him, right?   -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.95,variety,,0,0,0,,And I thought "is this kid retarded or something?..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.69,variety,,0,0,0,,That's all from Kurochan's parents
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.86,variety,,0,0,0,,So that's all from Kurochan's parents
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.59,variety,,0,0,0,,Kurochan's mother seems like a kind and earnest person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.16,variety,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his mother is really earnest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:41.07,variety,,0,0,0,,And she probably loves Kurochan so much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.50,variety,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's standing on his side
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.84,variety,,0,0,0,,So she probably hate both of us   -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.97,variety,,0,0,0,,No, no worries
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.97,variety,,0,0,0,,They hate Fujimon the most
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:55.91,variety,,0,0,0,,Eh? But actually, they should hate Kinoshita from TKO the most, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:55.91,variety-left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(9.714,193.714)}*Kinoshita from TKO is famous for mistreating juniors, and Kurochan once said that Kinoshita made him kneel down and scolded him while stepping on his head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.32,variety,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no need for Kurochan's mother to change channel then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:03.59,variety,,0,0,0,,However, since there's still a lot of mysteries left after interviewing with Kurochan's parents
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.72,variety,,0,0,0,,So, this time, we invited this person to today's show
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.66,variety,,0,0,0,,Please come in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.60,variety,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:17.13,variety,,0,0,0,,Here I am, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.10,variety,,0,0,0,,Kurochan, you watched it too, right? How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:23.31,variety,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I watched it, and I'm sure that the staffs are asking those questions with malicious intent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.64,variety,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:28.58,variety,,0,0,0,,They were like "Hey, Kurochan's mother, he's licking other's glass, how do you feel?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.21,variety,,0,0,0,,Is it necessary to ask those questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:33.55,variety,,0,0,0,,Well, but it's the fault of the person who licked it though
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:37.59,variety,,0,0,0,,Yeah well, although it's my fault, but I was actually so drunk, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.56,variety,,0,0,0,,So I don't even remember it, to be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.36,variety,,0,0,0,,You don't remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.23,variety,,0,0,0,,It's not in my memory*
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:45.00,variety-left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(35.429,166.286)}*The phrase "It's not in my memory (記憶にございません)" is always used as excuse by Japanese politicians
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.00,variety,,0,0,0,,That make things worse
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.86,variety,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can say if he put it like that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.67,variety,,0,0,0,,He's truly a useless person   -Yeah, a useless person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.57,variety,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not a useless person, listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.14,variety,,0,0,0,,Of course you are, you asked for $150,000 yen every month right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.34,variety,,0,0,0,,That was unbelievable   -It surely is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.44,variety,,0,0,0,,And $50,000 yen per month only until 2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.88,variety,,0,0,0,,You're already earning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.45,variety,,0,0,0,,In another perspective, I'm actually being dutiful towards my parents
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.35,variety,,0,0,0,,You two seems to be misunderstanding me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:06.62,variety,,0,0,0,,When parents don't need to worry about their children anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:11.82,variety,,0,0,0,,They'll think "oh, so the kids are fine on their own, they don't need us anymore", and may therefore even die sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.43,variety,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying my best to let them worry about me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:19.36,variety,,0,0,0,,And trick them into thinking "this kid won't be able to survive without us", and thus making them live a longer life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.60,variety,,0,0,0,,I've therefore asked for money on purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.00,variety,,0,0,0,,That's all from Kurokawa suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.00,variety,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not a suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:29.81,variety,,0,0,0,,You surely are a suspect   -No, it's not illegal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.34,variety,,0,0,0,,So that's what you think, Kurokawa member?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.38,variety,,0,0,0,,No, don't use the word member too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.88,variety,,0,0,0,,They both mean the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:35.88,variety-left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(35.429,166.286)}*When the suspect is a public figure, Japanese media refer to them as "members"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.85,variety,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're earning now, you should be the one to give them money
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.99,variety,,0,0,0,,You're earning a lot, right? You told me your annual income before
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.62,variety,,0,0,0,,I told you, but that's...   -You told me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:48.73,variety,,0,0,0,,But I need to pay taxes...   -Let Downtown know your annual income
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:49.33,variety,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.40,variety,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell them your annual income
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.37,variety,,0,0,0,,Eh? Did I tell you, Jinnai-san?   -Yes, you did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.00,variety,,0,0,0,,Eh? Really?   -Yes, you definitely told me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.80,variety,,0,0,0,,It was even in the news
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.67,variety,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?   -Yes, it was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.87,variety,,0,0,0,,Tell us about it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.77,variety,,0,0,0,,$960,000 yen for Kurochan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.18,variety,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that was a dull moment   -What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.31,variety,,0,0,0,,He probably did a wordplay Boke   -Yeah, 96 and Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.45,variety,,0,0,0,,Kuro has the same pronunciation with 96
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.85,variety,,0,0,0,,That's not what we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:15.42,variety,,0,0,0,,That was such a gentle Boke
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.42,variety,,0,0,0,,Just tell us then, Jinnai
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.19,variety,,0,0,0,,30,000,000 yen   -Why did you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.93,variety,,0,0,0,,It was in the news
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:26.00,variety,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, that's a dull moment from both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:29.77,variety,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not a dull moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:30.57,variety,,0,0,0,,That conversation was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.07,variety,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.84,variety,,0,0,0,,No, no, no way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.34,variety,,0,0,0,,Come on, Jinnai-san, don't drag me with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.94,variety,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who got dragged, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.01,variety,,0,0,0,,The news said that you're earning 30,000,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.18,variety,,0,0,0,,So scary, I wanna go home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.18,variety,,0,0,0,,This guy is earning 30,000,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.62,variety,,0,0,0,,Because there's a CM at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:49.59,variety,,0,0,0,,Anyway, did you buy any present or give any money to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.55,variety,,0,0,0,,Good question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.12,variety,,0,0,0,,No, not yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.09,variety,,0,0,0,,That's terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:58.46,variety,,0,0,0,,No, because we're in the time of Corona, and of course, I thought about doing something for them afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.77,variety,,0,0,0,,For example, what do you plan to do?   -Tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:01.80,variety,,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.14,variety,,0,0,0,,Make a promise with your parents now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:08.11,variety,,0,0,0,,I'll buy them a neckerchief
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.28,variety,,0,0,0,,It has been a while since I last heard that word, you're buying them a neckerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.28,variety,,0,0,0,,I'll buy them a neckerchief

